data.title: Leslie Jean Halbert James (1971
data.meta_description: Leslie G. James, 34, of Wolfanger Rd, Wayland, passed away early Sat morning, Dec 17, 2005, at her home after a courageous four and a half-year battle with cancer.  Leslie was born Jul 3, 1971, in North Hornell, the daughter of Leslie Halbert Jr. and Martha Birchard Glover. She grew up in Canaseraga and graduated from...
